  "description": [
    "SNJ Court Martial Play At Family Theatre Today The Naval Justice School Court Martial play The Trial of Rios anil Sullivan will be held today in the Family Theatre at 1210 for the present student class at the Justice School Vile cast will be comprised of officer civilian and enlisted personnel at the School as well as members from the student body The play will run approximate ly two hours and 10 minutes All personnel who have the available time are invited to attend A SPECIAL SENDOFF was Riven to Chief W J Anders after 20 years of service by the Naval Station Special Services Department LT James Gorman Special Services Officer presented the Chief with an engraved desk set and tendered to him the thanks of the Depart ment for his performance of duty Itctured are left to right Chief J 11 Webb Chief W J Anders IT J Gorman and LTJG J F Houten Assistant Special Services Officer The cast for the play is as follows Narrator LCDR A R Mater law Officer LCDR W 0 Miller Trial Counsel LT C A Cahill At Trial Counsel LUG H 0 lexfagr 111 Individual Couniel LT K K Bridget Detente"
  ],
